text: Kesmat Wkhayen () is a Tunisian drama television sitcom, in Tunisian Arabic, directed by Sami Fehri based on a script by Rafika Boujday. It is broadcast on El Hiwar El Tounsi channel during the month of Ramadan 2019 in Tunisia. == Synopsis == After their father died, Toutou is trying to con his half brother Hafnaoui out of his legal rights to heritage. == Cast == == References == Category:Drama television series
title: Kesmat Wkhayen
